nodes.text: Star Wars Rebels Look and Find

Star Wars Rebels Look and Find is a children's activity book that tasks readers with finding subjects in various crowded scenes adapted from the animated television series Star Wars Rebels, similar to the Where's Waldo? children's book series. It was illustrated by Art Mawhinney and published by Phoenix International Publications, Inc. on August 29, 2015, as part of its Look and Find series.
